products.Title: Pione Grape Chocolate Crunch (1 Piece)
products.Description: Indulge in a delicate bar that combines white chocolate, puffed malt, and the unique 'Black Pearl' grape. Crafted with Japan's renowned Pione grapes, the bar delights with a fragrant wine-like scent and a subtle, sweet grape flavor.
